Package: vbrecruit
Type: Package
Title: Calculate proportion of a cohort recruit each year based on VB growth
Version: 0.0999
Authors@R: person("Daniel", "Duplisea", email = "daniel.duplisea@dfo-mpo.gc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Based on Von Bertalanffy growth parameters, variation in growth and year of birth, 
  this calculates what percentage of a cohort's individuals will be at or above a certain length class each year.
  Special attention is drawn to the median, i.e. when half the cohort reaches a certain size.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
requires: rfishbase
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
